Invocation Name: utah's voice assistant expert
des:
***This skill is intended as a presentation for Utah Alexa Skills, a software development and hardware installation business based in Utah. This skill is in no way affiliated with or endorsed by Amazon or the Alexa Team***

Utah Alexa Skills is Utah's premier expert in setting up and configuring Amazon's Alexa voice assistant.

This skill is designed to introduce you to the services offered, and also provide a way for Utah Alexa Skills to contact you.

In order to utilize this skill to send a questionnaire email, you will need to enable permissions to access your email address. Your email address will only be used in-skill, and will not be stored or used for any other purposes.
